      <title>How to Manage Environment Variables</title>
      <link>https://carakan.net/blog/2019/09/how-to-manage-environment-variables/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2019 12:15:47 -0400</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://carakan.net/blog/2019/09/how-to-manage-environment-variables/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;In many projects that i have been working I want to manage GLOBAL&amp;rsquo;s variables, so
to do that use &lt;a href=&#34;https://direnv.net/&#34;&gt;direnv&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;to install (MacOS):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-zsh&#34; data-lang=&#34;zsh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;brew install direnv
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Now the project needs to create a file &lt;code&gt;.envrc&lt;/code&gt; like this:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-zsh&#34; data-lang=&#34;zsh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# Stripe Credentials&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;export STRIPE_PRIVATE_KEY&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;xxxxxxxxxxxx&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;export STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;entering in that directory &lt;code&gt;direnv&lt;/code&gt; asks to &lt;strong&gt;allow&lt;/strong&gt; the execution and use of
that variables, so:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-zsh&#34; data-lang=&#34;zsh&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;direnv allow .
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;And that&amp;rsquo;s it! you don&amp;rsquo;t need a custom solution for every programming language.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
